radiographic_examinations.findings: Mild linear atelectasis at the right lung base; moderate-to-large amount of inflammatory stranding in the upper abdomen centered around the pancreas; trace amount of fluid around the liver and in both paracolic gutters; multiple bilateral renal cystic lesions measuring up to 8.7 cm in the left kidney; urinary bladder moderately distended with fluid; prostate moderately enlarged; no osseous lesion suspicious for malignancy; no fracture.
